{"article_id":"f9K2zzSbbvAAh52L","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Previous debate audiences were much more pro-Rubio than this one .","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"Not so tonight , with bigger cheering sections for govs .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Impacted optics .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"- Guy Benson","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"( @ guypbenson )","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"February 7 , 2016","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Rubio survived Christie 's brutal assault ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"b/c Christie 's manner so aggressive likely to turn undecideds from him too","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"https : //t.co/ayq2jKaamA","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"- Matthew Continetti","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"( @ continetti )","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"February 7 , 2016 --","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"In desperate need of a strong showing in New Hampshire , three Republican governors stepped up","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and won tonight 's debate.","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"andall turned in outstanding performances ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"which may disrupt the state of play ahead of Tuesday 's votes .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"In a cycle","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that has been notably unkind to governors ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"these chief executives finally broke through .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"surging out of Iowa ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"endured a brutal opening segment ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"getting sliced and diced by Christie .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"The New Jerseyan attacked Rubio as scripted and untested ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"which Rubio parried well at first ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"but then proceeded to repeat almost the same verbatim defense of himself","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"as Christie poked and prodded .","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"With each similar Rubio response , Christie urged the audience to take note of how the Floridian was confirming the knock","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"the governor was advancing .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"This was Christie the prosecutor ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"puncturing a reluctant witness on the stand :","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"A cringeworthy stretch for Rubio .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Let 's see","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"if he suffers because of it .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"I should add","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that Rubio rebounded quite well later in the program ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"offering excellent and detailed answers on a host of questions","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"-- particularly in exchanges on ISIS and abortion .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"But the fact","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that Rubio was n't prepared to go several rounds with Christie ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"after a week of Christie telegraphing those very attacks ,","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"is mystifying .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"It was as if Rubio was ready to go toe-to-toe with Bush","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"( over attacks","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"that never came ) ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"and had n't anticipated Christie 's intense barrage .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"A big miscalculation .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"The Florida Senator can be very agile on his feet as a politician ;","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"in those opening minutes , he was not.","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"also started off a bit shaky ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"but recovered with a string of characteristically detailed answers across a spectrum of issues .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"Overall , he felt like less of a factor in this debate","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"than he did in recent forums .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"His victory dance","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"on beating the ethanol lobby in Iowa","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"was a sweet moment for fans of the free market .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"leading in the polls ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"had a decent night .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"He offered several good answers","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"( negotiating with terrorists comes to mind ) ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and a few bad ones","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"( he lost the eminent domain battle to Jeb ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"and was incoherent on foreign policy ) .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"If the polls are accurate ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Trump remains the odds-on frontrunner","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"heading into Tuesday ;","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"a good night for him.","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"overcame the awkward snafu during candidate introductions","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and did a nice job ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"connecting with voters on a personal level several times .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"His response to the Cruz 'rumor ' story was handled almost flawlessly","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"-- leading to one of his best moments , and one of Cruz 's toughest .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Overall , this was an informative and substantive debate ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"with a special home-team shout-out to Mary Katharine Ham for her superb questioning on healthcare , executive power and abortion .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"I 'll leave you with one X-factor","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"I believe","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"impacted this debate 's `` intangibles '' and optics :","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"ABC News reported after the debate","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"that Democrats","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"who were worried about Rubio 's post-Iowa ascension","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"were `` relieved `` by his early struggles .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Instead of solidifying his standing with a sharp , poised performance ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"Rubio stumbled in the opening minutes of the debate .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"That may be a `` teachable moment , ''","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"but how much will it cost him ?","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"And how much did his recovery negate his ugly start ? :","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"After tonight , Trump 's position as the leader in the clubhouse is unchanged","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"-- and the fight","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"over finishing in New Hampshire 's top tier","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"may have gotten a lot more interesting.","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"--","depth":2},{"id":91,"text":"Since I gave you video of Rubio","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"getting totally overmatched rhetorically by Christie ,","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"here 's his A+ answer on the pro-life question :","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"He also followed-up","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"by stating","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"although he views all life as sacred ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"he would sign pro-life legislation with exceptions as president .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Also , this analysis might be vindicated in the coming days ,","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"but that 's not how I watched that back-and-forth in real time .","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"I saw Christie draw political blood :","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":191,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":191,"left":113,"right":190,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":107,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":104,"right":106,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":109,"right":111,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":8,"relation":"expla